A toolkit targeting RedHat/Debian/etc ecosystems to perform menial tasks


#### perm

Set the permissions of a target file/folder based on defined rulesets

* Focus on compatibility of Unix/Linux users
  * This should be built-in as the default ruleset that is overridden by secondary rulesets
* Secondary rulesets
  * Apache (PHP, Python, Ruby)
  * cPanel/WHM
* Allow importing user-defined rulesets
  * Allows limiting the scope of what is required for direct inclusion

